
📦 Traderie Tools Overview

Enhances traderie.com with:
	•	✅ Ad-blocking
	•	📊 Rune-for-rune price analysis (Diablo II)
	•	📌 Bookmarking UI for listings & searches

🧩 Technologies
	•	Tampermonkey
	•	Vanilla JavaScript
	•	localStorage (for UI persistence)
	•	External data: rune_prices.json via GitHub
	•	DOM manipulation + MutationObserver

⸻

📁 Project Structure

traderie-tools.user.js       # Main Tampermonkey userscript
rune_prices.json             # External price mapping of runes → Ist value

🧾 rune_prices.json Format

{
  "pc_sc_nl": {
    "Jah Rune": { "ist_value": 10.38, "low_confidence": false },
    "Lo Rune": { "ist_value": 4.93, "low_confidence": true }
  }
}

	•	Keyed by: <platform>_<mode>_<ladder>
	•	Values: Normalized to Ist rune

⸻

🛠️ Script Features

1. 📵 Ad Blocker
	•	Selectors defined by category:

const SELECTOR_GROUPS = {
  google: ['iframe[src*="googlesyndication"]', ...],
  styled: ['div.sc-gfoqjT.gXykUj', ...],
  ...
};


	•	Persists enabled groups in localStorage
	•	Uses:
	•	MutationObserver to monitor DOM
	•	style tag for CSS-based hiding
	•	Manual removal via .remove()

Control API (window-bound):

window.traderieAdblock = {
  enable, disable, isEnabled
}

2. 💰 Rune Pricing
	•	Enabled via checkbox → localStorage
	•	Fetches external JSON (rune-to-Ist rates)
	•	Annotates listings with:
	•	+/-% difference
	•	Tooltip showing offer/ask Ist values

Key Functions:

fetchRunePrices(cb)         // Load price JSON
injectAll(prices)           // Inject into all visible listings
injectPercentAndTooltip()   // Per listing UI injection

	•	Uses:
	•	MutationObserver
	•	DOM parsing of .listing-name and .price-line
	•	parseRune() & parseAskGroups() utilities

⸻

3. 📌 Bookmarks
	•	UI for saving current URL as “listing” or “search”
	•	localStorage format:

[
  {
    "type": "search" | "listing",
    "name": "My Rune Search",
    "url": "https://traderie.com/d2r?prop_Mode=..."
  }
]

	•	UI includes:
	•	Editable names
	•	Click-to-visit
	•	Delete, rename

Relevant IDs:

#listingList, #searchList         // containers
#bookmarkName                     // input field
STORAGE_BOOKMARKS                // localStorage key


⸻

4. 🧩 UI Panel
	•	Draggable, resizable <div> with:
	•	Tabs: Bookmarks / Options
	•	Toggle state saved: open/closed, size, position
	•	Styled with custom CSS + Google Font (Alegreya Sans)
	•	Resizing and drag-persistence:
	•	Manual mousedown/mousemove tracking
	•	localStorage keys: traderieAppSize, traderieAppPosition

